content.rendered:
My summer must haves! I can’t get enough of my Zara Coated Jeans! Get a similar look here from Zara with a dark wash denim and boyfriend shirt. Pair with your favorite Louboutins, some stacked rings (like the ones seen here by Bvlgari) and Celine bag. And don’t forget to finish the look with your D’Lashes lipgloss and D’Wispy lashes and you’re ready for a day around town or a hot night out! To Purchase click on link of item.
